description: Erection of new development comprising of five blocks (with maximum heights of: Block A - eight storeys including basement; Block B - six storeys including basement; Blocks C, D and E - four storeys); to be used as 68 residential units (14 x one-bed, 39 two-bed, 2 x three-bed, 7 x four-bed and 6 x six bed) and a medical centre on the ground floor and basement levels of Block A; landscaping of central courtyard area and the excavation and layout of underground car parking.
decision_conditions:
CONDITION:  The affordable housing shall be completed and handed over to a Registered Social Landlord before 50% for the private residential units are occupied.

REASON:  To ensure the affordable housing element of the development is delivered within an acceptable time scale in accordance with policy H14 of the UDP 2002.
